dmca.title: Italy Information Site Wants Google to Delist Competitor
dmca.body:
To: Google, Inc,
Attn: Customer Support, DMCA Complaints 
[private]
Mountain View, CA 94043

May 26/04

1. The copyrighted work at issue are original news stories from www.zoomata.com used without permission in a newsletter, then archived online at www.onlyinitaly.com

2. stories used and archived in question:

"Hidden Costs of business in Italy" 
"Italians Patent
